Revision history for Perl extension Date::Holidays::US.

0.07 2024-12-30
   - Added National Day of Mourning for President Carter (Jan 9, 2025), Impacts 2025

0.06 2024-12-25
  - Added National Day of Mourning holidays, Impacts 1963, 1973, 1994, 2004, 2007, and 2018

0.05 2024-12-20
  - Fixed Inauguration Day logic when Jan 20th falls on a Sunday. Impacts 1985, 2013, 2041, 2069, 2097...

0.04 2024-12-20
  - Added Tuesday, December 24, 2024, the Day before Christmas Day per Executive Order

0.03 2022-09-06
  - Updated holidays function to dynamically calculate dates in the year as we expand is_holiday logic

0.02 2022-08-20
  - Updated Observance logic based on executive orders
  - Added GitHub meta links
  - Updated documentation

0.01 2022-08-19
  - original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
